## System Description

**EQMON (Apollo)** — AI-powered bearing expert chat platform for NAVSEA/DoD maritime predictive maintenance. Handles CUI under DFARS 252.204-7012.

- **Architecture:** PHP 8.4 web app + PostgreSQL 17 + Ollama AI backend
- **Hosting:** Single-tenant on-premises server (Artemis)
- **Network:** HTTPS/TLS 1.3 via nginx reverse proxy
- **Authentication:** JWT-based with role-based access control
- **Audit:** Append-only audit_events table with syslog fallback
- **Monitoring:** Real-time event correlation with 12 detection rules

